## ðŸ§© Key Architectural Patterns

### 1. Navigation Strategy
{% if libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["Expo Router"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **File-system Routing:** We use **Expo Router**.
- **Location:** Routes are defined in the `app/` directory.
- **Layouts:** Use `_layout.tsx` for defining stacks/tabs.
{% else %}
- **Component-based Routing:** We use **React Navigation**.
- **Stacks:** Defined in `src/navigation/`.
- **Typing:** strictly typed routes using `NativeStackScreenProps`.
{% endif %}

### 2. Styling System
{% if libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["NativeWind", "TailwindCSS"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **NativeWind:** We use Tailwind CSS classes via NativeWind.
- **Rule:** Use `className` property. Avoid `StyleSheet.create` unless you need dynamic values that NativeWind cannot handle.
{% elif libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["Tamagui"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **Tamagui:** Use the Tamagui compiler for performance. Use `Stack`, `Text`, `YStack` primitives.
{% else %}
- **StyleSheet:** We use the standard `StyleSheet.create`.
- **Theming:** All colors/spacing must come from `src/theme/`. No hardcoded hex values in components.
{% endif %}

### 3. State Management
{% if libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["Redux Toolkit"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **Global:** Redux Toolkit.
- **Async:** RTK Query for data fetching.
{% elif libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["Zustand"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **Global:** Zustand stores (split by feature).
{% else %}
- **Local:** `useState` / `useReducer`.
- **Global:** React Context (use sparingly to avoid re-renders).
{% endif %}

### 4. Data Persistence
{% if libraries | default([]) | select("in", ["MMKV"]) | list | length > 0 %}
- **Storage:** Use **react-native-mmkv** for synchronous, high-performance storage.
- **AsyncStorage:** Deprecated/Avoid (too slow).
{% else %}
- **Storage:** Async Storage (only for non-critical data).
{% endif %}